as01: NDC to RGB

Bruno Henrique Gouveia

Most of the code was given by Willem A. (Vlakkies) Schreuder, the shaders were implemented by me.

Time to complete: 1 hour

How to build: you just need to type the make.

Key bindings
  m/M        Cycle through shaders
  o/O        Cycle through objects
  p/P        Toggle between orthogonal & perspective projection
  a          Toggle axes
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit

You can also rotate using the mouse. You need to hold the left button and move your mouse to rotate.
